timeline.bodyText:
I don't really agree with throwing a PowsyblException in any case. You should do:
catch (IOException e) {
   throw new UncheckedIOException(e);
} catch (XMLStreamException e) {
    throw new UncheckedXmlStreamException(e);
}
You can write this only once at the end of the method (not twice)

